      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled as bilinear isotropic hardening with parameters derived from tensile coupon testing. Augmented Lagrangian contact at screw-rod and screw-vertebra interfaces captures the load transfer mechanism consistent with ASTM F1717 test configuration."
